author: David Hookstead
title: This Model’s Love Of The Outdoors Is Truly Inspiring
text:
(Photo by Vince Bucci/Getty Images) 5442451 
Model Sara Underwood is clearly a fan of the outdoors. 
She stands out from a generation of kids willing to sit around watching television and playing video games. Instead of doing that she chronicles her travels around the world exploring the outdoors. (SLIDESHOW: 67 Times Abigail Ratchford Was Almost Naked) 
She even captioned one of her outdoor photos, “I’ve always been more keen on the mountains and the country, but the ocean is really winning me over.” (SLIDESHOW: THIS BLONDE BOMBSHELL MIGHT BE THE HOTTEST MODEL ON INSTAGRAM)
